[src:service-mesh-deep/load-balancing-computing] The balancer polls servers for application layer health and removes failed servers from the pool.
[src:service-mesh-deep/load-balancing-computing] The balancer stores static content so that some requests can be handled without contacting the servers.
[src:service-mesh-deep/load-balancing-computing] Some balancers can arbitrarily modify traffic on the way through.
